		   <br><img src=/shared/transp.gif width=135 border=0 height=1></td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>I've only been playing for about a month.&nbsp;&nbsp;I've finished my armor and weapon quests from the guildmaster.  I was wondering where can I take my level 12 to level up fairly fast, and what is a good trade for a druid?&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Sheila Sims<br>Phoenix AZ USA</td></td></tr>
		 <tr><td colspan=2 class=mform><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >1 Replies</td></tr></table></td></tr>
